from the local loony bin.

41:36.294 --> 41:39.104
You know, you're lucky
my mother's not here.

41:39.164 --> 41:42.543
She wouldn't let anyone
blaspheme, not even me.

41:42.600 --> 41:45.706
You're right, your mother's
a very Godly woman

41:45.770 --> 41:50.719
and she prays for you to come
to me every day, Charlie.

41:50.775 --> 41:53.085
Don't break your
mother's heart, Charlie.

41:53.144 --> 41:55.055
Shut up!
Just shut up!

41:55.113 --> 41:57.093
Give me your gun,
Charlie.

41:57.148 --> 41:58.650
<i>Give me your gun.</i>

