I would have left it a ruin,

42:30.615 --> 42:33.824
<i>a monument
to God's cruelty.</i>

42:33.885 --> 42:38.231
Do you think that's
the way Timothy sees it?

42:38.289 --> 42:42.965
<i>Anywhere he looked,
he saw my love.</i>

42:43.027 --> 42:45.667
I don't wanna
talk about him.

