pass through the eye of a needle

56:57.548 --> 57:02.520
<i>than for a rich man to enter
the kingdom of God.</i>

57:05.722 --> 57:09.295
Why don't you just
leave the guy alone?

57:09.359 --> 57:11.236
Why don't you leave
Bruno alone?

57:11.295 --> 57:12.603
<i>Yeah!</i>

57:13.263 --> 57:16.244
Why are you treating me
like the bad guy?

57:16.300 --> 57:19.804
You know how many people
his heroin kills every year?

57:19.870 --> 57:23.818
Yes, and I know
every one of their names.

57:23.874 --> 57:26.855
So you should hate him
as much as I do.

57:26.910 --> 57:29.186
<i>Burl don't.</i>

57:29.246 --> 57:32.693
Sadly, if he doesn't repent,
I will be forced

57:32.749 --> 57:35.889
by that decision of his
to judge him.

57:35.952 --> 57:40.332
But don't think that I take
pleasure in that, I don't.

57:40.391 --> 57:44.134
So what are you saying?
He can go to heaven?

57:44.194 --> 57:47.141
Yes, if he repents.

57:47.197 --> 57:50.906
<i>I'd be thrilled.</i>

57:50.968 --> 57:54.609
<i>Well, count me out then
because I ain't going anywhere</i>

57:54.671 --> 57:58.953
where he's going except maybe
to prison to visit him.

57:59.009 --> 58:05.221
<i>Ric, can I
ask you a question?</i>

58:05.282 --> 58:07.387
Can I stop you?

58:07.451 --> 58:14.027
