killed her.

59:21.792 --> 59:25.706
<i>So now you're
going to kill him?</i>

59:25.762 --> 59:27.742
<i>If that's what it takes.</i>

59:27.798 --> 59:32.110
- To do what?
- To bring him to justice!

59:32.169 --> 59:35.048
<i>Ric, you love
that word justice.</i>

59:35.105 --> 59:36.379
<i>You don't know
what it means.</i>

59:36.440 --> 59:39.717
<i>Justice has no place
for illegal wire-taps,</i>

59:39.776 --> 59:42.450
planted evidence,
perjured testimony.

59:42.512 --> 59:47.188
<i>Hey! I'm just trying to
level the playing field here.</i>

59:47.251 --> 59:49.527
Guys like Bruno have
all the money they need

59:49.586 --> 59:56.367
<i>to hire the best lawyers,
buy half the judges and juries.</i>

59:56.426 --> 01:00:01.500
<i>If we didn't cut some corners,
we wouldn't make case one.</i>

01:00:01.565 --> 01:00:04.808
<i>The ends don't
justify the means.</i>

01:00:04.868 --> 01:00:06.142
Says who?!

01:00:06.203 --> 01:00:08.114
You?

01:00:08.172 --> 01:00:11.415
Your way doesn't work.

01:00:11.475 --> 01:00:14.513
The meek didn't
inherit the earth.

01:00:14.578 --> 01:00:20.654
