01:00:39.303 --> 01:00:41.783
<i>But it's not
too late, Ric.</i>

01:00:41.838 --> 01:00:44.375
Behold me.

01:00:44.441 --> 01:00:49.288
<i>I stand at the door of
your heart, and I knock.</i>

01:01:00.590 --> 01:01:05.562
<i>It's your supplier, again.</i>

