This is him.

01:01:08.064 --> 01:01:09.372
Hello?

01:01:16.173 --> 01:01:18.153
Will you still
be here today?

01:01:20.310 --> 01:01:23.291
<i>But you still will be
here today, right?</i>

01:01:26.816 --> 01:01:30.127
Late r?

